          <text><![CDATA[<p> <b>Practice of Law Technical Clarification Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Fair Debt Collection Practices Act to exclude from the definition of &quot;debt collector&quot; any law firm or licensed attorney engaged in litigation to collect a debt on behalf of a client, if such legal action complies with applicable rules of civil procedure. </p> <UL><UL> </UL> </UL> <BR>]]></text>
